{"tid":1218915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係基督徒，好想分享一啲聖經鼓勵大家","createTime":"2019-06-13T17:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T17:11:50.000Z","uid":204385,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b9f5d2d70ebf48dd339f73b21420f8305f6ee3d0","tid":1218915,"uid":204385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:07:03.000Z","msg":"我知實會有人會話我乘機傳福音，同埋經文想講既野未必係咁既意思(因為應該要睇埋上下文)，但係真係好想用聖經同香港人集氣。<br />\n<br />\n「我把這些事告訴你們，是要使你們在我裡面有平安。在世上你們有患難，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但你們放心，我已經勝了這世界</span></span>。&rdquo;」<br />\n‭‭約翰福音‬ ‭16:33‬ ‭CNV‬‬<br />\n<br />\n「耶和華是應當稱頌的， 他沒有容讓敵人把我們當作獵物撕裂。 我們像雀鳥從捕鳥的人的網羅裡逃脫； 網羅破裂，我們就逃脫了。 我們的幫助在於耶和華的名， 他是造天地的主。」<br />\n‭‭詩篇‬ ‭124:6-8‬ ‭CNV‬‬<br />\n<br />\n「我必親自牧養我的羊，親自使牠們躺臥。這是主耶和華的宣告。 迷失的，我必尋找；被趕散的，我必領回；受傷的，我必包紮；患病的，我必養壯；<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肥壯的，我卻要除滅。</span></span>我也必按著公正牧養牠們。」<br />\n‭‭以西結書‬ ‭34:15-16‬ ‭CNV‬‬<br />\n<br />\n「耶和華的名是應當稱頌的， 從今時直到永遠！ <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從日出之地到日落之處</span></span>， 耶和華的名是應當讚美的！」<br />\n‭‭詩篇‬ ‭113:2-3‬ ‭RCUV‬‬<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">sing hallelujah to the lord</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3665caa3c54144bad81aabaa465d4e7b1e564f","tid":1218915,"uid":90610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"Okay!!<br />\n聽你地講一次經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac76d706bda414e3093635fa9d91f5ebf25c2f5","tid":1218915,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco